show_title: GM Farcaster ep241 Monday May 5, 2025 chatting FarCon and Clanker
text:
There is no "shadowbanning" on Warpcast. 

If you make a top-level cast, it will show up in the feeds of everyone who follows you. 

You don't have to take my word for it. Cast something, take a friends phone and scroll to the bottom of their feed. Your cast will show up at some point - it will be higher up if they interact with you a lot, and lower down if they don't.

Clanker has recently become aware of information concerning @proxystudio.eth's conduct during his previous employment. Following these revelations, @proxystudio.eth has decided to part ways with Clanker, effective immediately.

We want to assure our community, partners, and stakeholders that Clanker's operations and assets remain unaffected by this situation. This matter relates solely to activities that occurred prior to his involvement with our organization.

show_title: GM Farcaster ep241 Monday May 5, 2025 chatting FarCon and Clanker
text:
These past few days have been extremely tough on so many levels. The outpour of support has reassured me that the Clanker ecosystem has incredible strength and I will continue to devout all of my energy into building towards our goal of innovation through collaboration, empowering projects in an equitable manor for believers & dreamers. 

Clanker is more than one person and a single team. I‚Äôm incredibly confident that we‚Äôll bounce back stronger than ever and our ability to gather attention towards projects will continue. Everyone will have to step up to fill this void, starting with myself, our team internally, and everyone in & around the ecosystem. 

As a first time founder being thrown into this complex situation, I promise to lead with pride, integrity, and strive to always do the right thing, building in public and taking ecosystem feedback to provide tools to help creators thrive. 

Thank you, from the bottom of my heart.
